  (text "KEY MATRIX  5x12 (59 keys, COL2ROW diodes)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 20.32 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "4493fa45-2326-5081-95c2-500e032a1a5a"))
  (text "MCU -- RP2040 (VERIFY pin numbers before fab, see file header)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 96.52 100.33 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "4be5341a-c0a1-5cef-aaac-a42a9188514c"))
  (text "RP2040 minimum system (core regulator, 12MHz xtal, QSPI flash)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 96.52 63.5 0) (effects (font (size 3.0 3.0) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "a18430c1-d7e4-5408-9861-6f92419a89e2"))
  (text "Wireless (CYW43439, BLE-only) -- crystal/pinout/power topology verified against datasheet 002-30348 Rev *D; RF matching values still VERIFY (vendor/antenna-specific)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 96.52 114.3 0) (effects (font (size 2.5 2.5) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "f2ab97a7-4de2-54c3-8c9f-1176207c269b"))
  (text "Per-key RGB -- SK6812MINI-E x59, serpentine chain (must match Sources/smk/RGBLighting.swift ledChainIndex)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 45.72 0) (effects (font (size 3.0 3.0) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "f4992e9e-866a-5658-bba2-d87d6b7f7a3e"))
  (text "RGB power budget (calculated from the SK6812MINI-E datasheet, 12mA/channel x 3 x 59 LEDs = 2.12A max at full white): fed from VSYS, NOT the 3.3V LDO (AP2112K-3.3 isn't remotely rated for this). D60 (B5819W, ~1A avg rating) IS in this path when USB-powered and WOULD be exceeded by 2.12A -- firmware must cap brightness/concurrent-on count well below full-white-all-keys regardless of power source. Also VERIFY: SK6812MINI-E's own datasheet specs VDD 3.7-5.5V, and VSYS (Li-ion battery) can sag below 3.7V well within normal discharge range -- LEDs may misbehave on a low battery even with brightness capped. Level shifter keeps DIN threshold margin safe across the VSYS voltage range (separate from the VDD-minimum concern above)." (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 38.1 0) (effects (font (size 1.6 1.6) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "1ca5d67a-e229-5e2d-b159-c79c88fc070b"))
  (text "USB-C  (charge + native USB)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 219.71 105.41 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "6991944b-fc17-5425-a1f8-1c93cd507ac2"))
  (text "Li-ion charger 500mA" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 287.02 105.41 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "bfba07cc-5803-5e91-b8a9-0120f1e8b538"))
  (text "Power path + 3.3V LDO + ON/OFF" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 340.36 105.41 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "120bce2d-e71e-5c60-85c4-3c86ea0e3b1d"))
  (text "VBAT sense + RESET + BOOTSEL" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 391.16 105.41 0) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "cfbbdad4-3590-5479-b536-62d354793eda"))
  (text "GPIO map (VERIFY pin numbers, see file header):  ROW0-4 = GPIO0-4   COL0-11 = GPIO5-16   RGB_GPIO = GPIO17   VBAT_SENSE = GPIO26/ADC0   BT UART/ctrl (GPIO18-23, 28) = CYW43439 BLE link (see wireless section)" (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 95.25 0) (effects (font (size 2.0 2.0) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "6f6dbdfa-f0a0-5b50-89f9-6bc33923f3dd"))
  (text "Charging works with power switch OFF (charger connects before switch).  BOOTSEL+RESET = USB mass-storage bootloader mode (VERIFY)." (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.4 100.33 0) (effects (font (size 2.0 2.0) (thickness 0.3) bold) (justify left bottom)) (uuid "a2819d82-a568-53fa-99e7-0b1ccb81d3a9"))
